name: TrustSwap
description: Established in July 2020, TrustSwap Launchpad is a leading Web3 Launchpad and IDO service, achieving the #1 spot on Cryptorank in 2023 for All-time High Returns and Average Returns. It provides a comprehensive platform for blockchain enthusiasts, having launched over 55 projects with a collective fundraising of over $70 million. TrustSwap, the parent company of The Crypto App and Team Finance, offers exclusive project allocations for members with a SWAP score of 4,000+, alongside a suite of services including crypto portfolio tracking, token and liquidity locks, and vesting-as-a-service.
